@node Context
@chapter Context Module

The context module wraps @code{cairo_t}, the central object of Cairo.
Every drawing operation goes through a context bound to a surface.

Full C API reference:
@uref{https://www.cairographics.org/manual/cairo-cairo-t.html}.

@example
(use-modules (cairog))
@end example

